Speaker1: Extra Bet, madan/sir, with X. Your current link is Extrabet944.com. I’ve already sent you the link via SMS. You can log in through the link choose either the free spin of free bet options to create your account.
Speaker2: I’ve already made a deposit, not even half an hour ago.
Speaker1: Let me check it right away with your phone number. Please hold for a moment while I check. Yes, I see that you already have an account. I’ll now check if you have a gesture bonus. Additionally, I have shared the updated link to our site with you. Currently, no bonuses are visible on your account. I’m noting down your username, and you’ll be notified via SMS or WhatsApp. Alternatively, if you contact live support, they’ll inform you of any gifts or bonuses you may have.
Speaker2: I usually get a message when there’s a gift but since I had some losses, I was planning to deposit, but I didn’t.
Speaker1: You can get a 10% deposit bonus on our site without any wagering requirements. Alternatively, you can receive a 10% cashback bonus, which is also wager-free. In case of a loss, a personal assistant bonus can also be added proportional to your deposit.
Speaker2: I’ve had a loss right now, but you’re not assigning such a bonus.
